{% set shorttype = 'cg' %}

A warm welcome to the W3C {{ group.name }}!

Together we work on improving WebViews for everyone. All documents and projects can be found in our GitHub organization at:
  https://www.github.com/WebView-CG

The website https://caniwebview.com is an informational site where we document the state of WebView support across platforms.

More links for important resources:

You can find information about the {{ group.name }} linked from:
  https://www.w3.org/groups/{{ shorttype }}/{{ group.shortname }}/

For meetings, check the group calendar at
  https://www.w3.org/groups/{{ shorttype }}/{{ group.shortname }}/calendar/

W3C also has an informal Slack workspace and you are invited to join the #webview-cg channel there. To join, see:
  https://www.w3.org/slack-w3ccommunity-invite

If you have not already done so, please link your GitHub account to your W3C account using
  https://www.w3.org/users/myprofile/connectedaccounts/
If you do not have a GitHub account, we highly encourage you to create one! 

All participants in the {{ group.name }} are expected to behave in accordance with the W3C Code of Conduct
  https://www.w3.org/policies/code-of-conduct/

If you have any questions or concerns, you can reach the {{ group.name }} chair directly.

We are excited to have you!
